            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="960.810" end="x">During the period of demobilization a whole group of young military men decided to organize a kind of group for common action because we still hoped that resistance will continue in North Africa.<note n="14"><span class="note">At the outbreak of the war, France controlled the countries of Morocco, Algeria and Tunisia in North Africa. The desire of Mr. Bramson and some other young military men to continue the struggle against the Germans from North Africa is indicative of their patriotic determination and martial spirit.</span><sup><a href="#note_14">14</a></sup></note></span>
