            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">But this was not important since my name sounds sufficiently French—it was of no importance.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
