            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">Bramson [pronounced in French], and so that was not important.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">Well.</span>
