            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">And to him the question of a Jew or not a Jew was of no interest whatsoever. So when he came to the section where the questionnaire dealt with race or religion, he all at once asked me such a question: "Are you a Protestant or a Catholic?"</span>
        </li>
