            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">All the others were found by the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> with the help of the management of the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> and they were all shot.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">Where were they shot?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">They were shot wherever it would happen. They were killed—when they would catch one, they would lead him outside the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>, and they would shoot him just any place. A few of them, since the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> were vexed, were hanged, and this in spite [of the fact] that they were sentenced to be shot.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">And where did they hang them?</span>
