            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">I was in the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> . . . I spent there fifteen months.<note n="51"><span class="note">The fifteen months were from early 1944 until April 1945.</span><sup><a href="#note_51">51</a></sup></note></span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">So. What were you doing there?</span>
        </li>
