            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="x" end="x">When they departed, they left only a small detail of <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> who were to set fire to the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>, and throw all [unintelligible].</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="x" end="x">To kill the people?</span>
