        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="4852.792" end="x">[In Russian] You told me that at the end you were not anymore in <a class="placename" href="#vothC15" type="camp">Buchenwald</a>. How did that happen?</span>
