            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="6932.011" end="x">And in this letter Goethe states, "When I am in a sad mood, I go up to <a class="placename" href="#vothC15" type="camp">Buchenwald</a>, I approach my oak and look at it and hope . . . "</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="6949.157" end="x">. . . returns.</span>
