            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Jacques Bramson</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#bramsonJ" start="6949.907" end="x">". . . returns to me. It is so mighty, so strong, that to me it is an embodiment of the might of our people."</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
